description:
The wait is finally over. After months of speculation and rumour, its time to find out if Deadpool & Wolverine was worth the wait. Join me, MauLer, Robot Head, Reaper and Echo Chamberlain as we talk about it.

title: Open Bar #105 - Deadpool & Wolverine, Twisters, Cobra Kai S6
